OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness
OL,7,Fin places. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be mainly dry although a little
OL,9,Fdrizzle possible along the west coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA dry day on Thursday with
OL,12,Fsome bright or sunny spells developing
OL,13,Fby afternoon but still some cloud
OL,14,Faround. Warm.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry and cloudy on Friday, perhaps the
OL,18,Fodd light shower at first. Rain
OL,19,Fspreading southeast on Saturday, drier
OL,20,Fwith a few showers later. Mainly dry
OL,21,Fon Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
